---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="SocialProof for Sleep Consultants — Testimonials That Book Exhausted Parents | SocialProof"
  description="Collect and display authentic client testimonials for your sleep consulting practice. Let success stories sell your services to desperate parents. Free to start."
>
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">For Sleep Consultants</p>
        <h1>Parents are desperate. Real success stories close them instantly.</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">When a parent hasn't slept in months, they don't want to be sold to. They want proof it actually works. SocialProof captures your clients' "finally slept through the night" moments and displays them where desperate parents can find them.</p>
        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
          <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="btn btn-secondary">See how it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pain">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why sleep consultant social proof is underutilized</h2>
        <div class="pain-grid">
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>😤 Clients don't think to leave reviews</h3>
            <p>They're finally sleeping. They're grateful — but they're also busy. Asking for a Google review six weeks later gets silence, even from your happiest families.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>📸 The results are invisible</h3>
            <p>A sleeping baby isn't Instagrammable. The transformation happens in private. That's exactly why you need written testimonials — it's the only way to show the proof.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>🔗 High skepticism, high stakes</h3>
            <p>Sleep training is controversial territory. Worried parents have been burned by generic advice. Real names, real results, real quotes from real clients are the only thing that moves them.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="solution">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>SocialProof fixes this in 3 steps</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            <strong>Send a collect link</strong>
            <p>After the first week of a child sleeping through the night, text or email parents a link. "Would you share your experience in 2 minutes?" Strike when they're overwhelmed with gratitude.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Approve with one click</strong>
            <p>Review submissions in your dashboard. Approve the testimonials that capture the real transformation: nights of sleep gained, family stress reduced, sanity restored.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Embed on your site</strong>
            <p>One script tag on your services or about page. Works on any site builder — Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, Kajabi.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Built for Sleep Consultants</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>⭐ Star ratings + text</h3>
            <p>Capture the whole story — not just a star rating but the parent's journey from exhausted to rested. That narrative converts searchers into clients.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📷 Family photos</h3>
            <p>Let clients share a photo. A happy, rested family is the most powerful ad you'll ever run.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🎨 Matches your brand</h3>
            <p>Customize colors and layout. Calm, professional, reassuring — just like your practice.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📱 Easy mobile form</h3>
            <p>Parents can fill it in 60 seconds on their phone. Short, simple, and designed to capture the "it finally worked" moment.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🔒 Privacy-first</h3>
            <p>You control every testimonial before it goes public. Clients can share first names only. You own the data — not Google, not Yelp.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🆓 Free forever tier</h3>
            <p>1 active widget, unlimited collections. Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card to start.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing-cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
        <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. Pro is $9/mo for unlimited everything.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get started free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
